{"tid":1968164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口嫌體正直！美國若討疫情索賠…84%支那人竟自願割地「舉四肢同意」","createTime":"2020-04-11T12:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T12:58:04.000Z","uid":32511,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2ef42a0a2f9e177d41f104523f2286d6875369","tid":1968164,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/10/2497007-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F10%2F2497007-XXL.jpg&h=c1d78904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（COVID-19，新型冠狀病毒）疫情衝擊全球經濟，中國被視為主要發源地，美國總統川普甚至不甩武漢肺炎正名為「新冠肺炎」，多次堅稱就是「中國病毒（ChineseVirus）」。美國華人媒體《新高地》近日在推特進行網路民調，「中國若要向美國割地賠償疫情損失，你願意將你的家鄉割給美國嗎」？驚人的是，高達84.1%的網友竟然表態願意。<br />\n <br />\n根據《新高地》網路民調，題目為「疫情結束後，美國必然向中國提出索賠，而中國又沒錢，假如中國政府提出願意割地賠款時，你願意將你的家鄉所在省割讓給美國嗎」？結果顯示84.1%願意、10.9%不願意、4.9%不好說。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到投票一面倒，許多人表態「願意成為美國人」，還有網友表示，「肯定割讓啊，這樣我就有美國公民的一切福利了，超便宜物價，高福利保障，還有可以獲得免簽全球的美國護照」、「估計90%國人都願意，突然不動就成美國公民了，享受美國的福利待遇，多美的好事」、「舉四肢同意，代表我全家」、「你提出割地，美國還不一定要呢。不過我們的鄰居俄流氓，可就不一定了」。"},{"pid":"85a72677eb10fa24b3e9bb246d74bef5c9c25459","tid":1968164,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe08d8fb2c8abf04c5d675eb81f782a6eafb79e","tid":1968164,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:48:41.000Z","msg":"[CCTVB戰線] 美國網民玩死電視台嘅成功例子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avicQNU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avicQNU</a>"},{"pid":"15e2dd73808c42f7a14a5f135c940bcf05f68840","tid":1968164,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"有綠卡拎, 支那人爭住含美國撚LA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525e1a46dadebdf3954c9042f52a43296c04e584","tid":1968164,"uid":20170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">超便宜物價，高福利保障，還有可以獲得免簽全球的美國護照</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三樣都唔係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但美國喺佢哋眼中原來係咁"},{"pid":"7ef367eb8e0d0d6f5c76e94ee239aacb8073f2db","tid":1968164,"uid":126621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人口裡說不<br />\n身體卻很誠實"},{"pid":"55835f0af42c0fcbd0f1d84484b89072f2c65ba8","tid":1968164,"uid":203431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:58:04.000Z","msg":"Sir this way pls <br />\nChoose me choose me"}]}